author: fmeschbe
msg: Introduce a LoginModulePluginFactory to be able to create new plugin instances for each login request. Previously only a single service instance has been used for all requests and thus would prevent actualy state keeping during the login process. To this avail the lifecycle methods init, abort, and commit from the LoginModule interface have been added.
